        <abstract> 
<p>Hopes Murray will publish after seeing MS [of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>].</p>  
<p>Demurs at JDH’s saying that CD changes climate to account for migration of bugs, flies, etc. "<hi rend="italic">We</hi> do nothing of the sort; for <hi rend="italic">we</hi> rest on scored rocks, old moraines, arctic shells, and mammifers." Has given up the Lyellian doctrine as insufficient to explain all changes in climate; CD has no theory about the cause of the cold.</p> 
        </abstract>
